231
00:15:40,773 --> 00:15:44,528
Okay, half in this van,
half in this one. Let's go.

232
00:15:45,695 --> 00:15:48,494
Have a good trip.
Bring me back something French.

233
00:15:51,242 --> 00:15:55,042
