it leaves in 45 minutes.

234
00:15:55,246 --> 00:15:56,498
Think positive!

235
00:15:56,706 --> 00:15:58,629
You be positive. I'll be realistic.

236
00:15:58,791 --> 00:16:02,386
Ma'am. Ma'am.
Excuse me, your power is fixed...

237
00:16:02,587 --> 00:16:06,217
