550
00:48:46,507 --> 00:48:49,101
<i>Keep the change, you filthy animal.</i>

551
00:48:51,011 --> 00:48:52,763
- Cheapskate.
-Hey.

552
00:48:52,972 --> 00:48:55,270
<i>I'm gonna give you
to the count of 10...</i>

553
00:48:55,474 --> 00:48:57,852
<i>...to get your ugly, yellgwm</i>

554
00:48:58,102 --> 00:49:00,196
<i>...no-good keister off my property...</i>

555
00:49:00,396 --> 00:49:02,524
